本文档针对USDC/ETH 0.05% pool进行分析，内容涵盖

  • 0 数据预处理
  • 1 基于position的分析
    含本金、时间间隔、累计收益、transaction cost、fee earned、wealth change、价格区间宽度分析
  • 2 基于LP的分析

本文档结论主要有：

  1. 年化较高的position特点
  • fee earned年化更高
  • wealth change基本为正值
  • 持有时间短（基本短于2天）
  • transaction cost总额区别不大,但年化小
  • 价格区间相对较窄
  1. 年化收益率高的LP特点
  • fee earned年化相对更高
  • transaction cost总额区别不大,但年化小
  • 大部分参与时间短于2周
  • wealth change为正

Note:

  • This file is used to help convert the values in the block-chain (as shown in the original table) to the true and meaningful values in the real world, so that it can be used in the data analysis.

  • Let $Value_{chain}$ denote the value in chain and $Value_{real}$ denote the value in the real world.

  • ### event_name:

    • Mint: add liquidity and deposit tokens
    • Burn: remove liquidity. Generally one burn is followed by one collect, and when 2 burn is followed by one collect, the second burn is to delete the token address from NFT Manager.
    • Collect: collect fee earned and the remaining principal when the burn action is implemented. (transaction cost is paid separately)
    • Swap: exchange one token for another

  • ### Timestamp (seconds): Unix style timestamp. $t_{chain} = 31556926*t_{year}+ 2629743*t_{month}+86400*c+3600*t_{hour}+60*t_{min}+t_{sec}$ $t_{real}=t_{year}+1970,t_{month},t_{day},t_{hour},t_{min},t_{sec}$

  • ### gasUsed: The total gas that is consumed by the transaction.

    $$value_{chain}=value_{real}$$

  • ### gasPrice: The gas price at the historical moment. $$G_{chain}=63800000000,G_{real}=G_{chain}\times 10^{-9}=63.8Gwei,$$

    ( $1 Ether = 10^9 Gwei = 10^{18} Wei$)

  • ### transactionCost: The total transaction cost = gasUsed $\times$ gasPrice.

    $$Tcost_{chain}=324102341200000000Wei= 0.3241023412ETH \times 10^{18}$$

  • ### tickSpacing: The amount of required tick separation, realized in multiples of tickSpacing e.g., a tickSpacing of 3 requires ticks to be initialized every 3rd tick i.e., ..., -6, -3, 0, 3, 6, ...

  • ### fee tier:0.05%, 0.30%, and 1% $$t_{chain}=3000=0.3\%* 10^{6}$$

  • ### Tick converted to price: Token 0 is USDC, Token 1 is ETH $$Price=\frac{T_1}{T_0}$$

    $$P_{chain}= 1.0001^{tick}=P_{real}\times 10^{12}$$

  • ### Price converted to tick: Token 0 is USDC, Token 1 is ETH

    $P_{chain}$ is in type of sqrtPriceX96. $$P_{chain}=\sqrt{1.0001^{tick}}\times 2^{96}$$ $$Tick=\lfloor \log_{1.0001}(P_{chain}/2^{96})\times 2\rfloor$$

  • ### amount0_delta/amount1_delta:

    • for swap: the delta of token balance of the pool
    • for mint: how much token was required for the minted liquidity
    • for burn: The amount of token withdrawn

    $USDC: \Delta T_{0}^{chain}=50000000000=50000\times 10^6=\Delta T_0^{real }\times 10^6$

    $ETH: \Delta T_{1}^{chain} =9.20548411925653\times 10^{18}=\Delta T_1^{real}\times 10^{18}$

  • ### liquidity: The virtual liquidity of the pool after swap. $$L_{chain}=L_{real}\times 10^{12}$$

  • ### liquidity_delta: The amount of liquidity to be removed or added.

$$\Delta L_{chain}=\Delta L_{real}\times 10^{12}$$$$\Delta T_0=L (\frac{1}{\sqrt{P_{current}}}-\frac{1}{\sqrt{P_{upper}}})$$$$\Delta T_1=L(\sqrt{P_{current}}-\sqrt{P_{lower}})$$
  • ### Original file columns
Column Name Description
txn_hash Transaction hash, it is used to uniquely identify each transaction.
timestamp Unix style timestamp. Conversion tool: https://www.unixtimestamp.com/index.php.
gasUsed The total gas that is consumed by the transaction. [Unit: Wei]
gasPrice The gas price at the historical moment. [Unit: Wei]
transaction_cost The total transaction cost. transaction_cost = gasUsed x gasPrice. [Unit: Wei x Wei]
tokenId The ID of the non-fungible token, representing a unique position range (a combination of "tickerLower" and "tickUpper")
tickLower The lower boundary of the position range. Actual lower price boundary = 1.0001^tickLower/10^12.
tickUpper The upper boundary of the position range. Actual upper price boundary = 1.0001^tickUpper}/10^12.
amount0 The amount of fee collected from token 0 (base currency) by the Collect Event.
amount1 The amount of fee collected from token 1 (quote currency) by the Collect Event.
liquidity The liquidity of the pool after the transaction. Liquidity = sqrt(amount of token 0 x amount of token 1)
paid0 The amount of token 0 paid for the "Flash Swap".
paid1 The amount of token 1 paid for the "Flash Swap".
amount0_delta The change of the amount of token 0.
amount1_delta The change of the amount of token 1.
liquidity_delta The change of the liquidity of the pool.
sqrtPriceX96 The ratio of sqrt(amount of token 1 / amount of token 0).The relationship of sqrtPriceX96 and tick is: 1.0001 ^ (tick / 2) x 2 ^ 96 = sqrtPriceX96.
tick Representing the price. Actual price = 1.0001 ^ tick.
event_type Possible values: "AddLiquidity", "RemoveLiquidity", "Swap", "Flash". "Flash" will be integrated to "Swap" later.
from For mint, collect and burn, the from address is the address of the liquidity provider.

transaction = pd.read_csv(indir+'\\'+file, encoding = 'utf-8',low_memory=False)
transaction['transactionCost'] = transaction['transactionCost'].apply(lambda x:int(x)/10**18)
transaction['liquidity_delta'] = transaction['liquidity_delta'].apply(lambda x:float(x)/10**12)
transaction['amount1_delta'] = transaction['amount1_delta'].apply(lambda x:float(x)/10**18)
transaction['amount1_collected'] = transaction['amount1_collected'].apply(lambda x:float(x)/10**18)
mint = transaction[transaction['event_name']=='Mint'].index
burn = transaction[transaction['event_name']=='Burn'].index
collect = transaction[transaction['event_name']=='Collect'].index
swap = transaction[transaction['event_name']=='Swap'].index
transaction['dt'] = np.nan
transaction.loc[mint,'dt'] = transaction.loc[mint,'timeStamp'].diff()
transaction.loc[burn,'dt'] = transaction.loc[burn,'timeStamp'].diff()
transaction.loc[collect,'dt'] = transaction.loc[collect,'timeStamp'].diff()
transaction.loc[swap,'dt'] = transaction.loc[swap,'timeStamp'].diff()
transaction.loc[:,'tick'].ffill(inplace=True)
transaction['p_current'] = transaction['sqrtPriceX96'].apply(lambda x:math.log(float(x)/2**96,1.0001)*2)
transaction['p_current'].ffill(inplace=True)
transaction['burn_dt'] = np.nan
transaction['fee_earned_token0'] = np.nan
transaction['fee_earned_token1'] = np.nan
transaction['transaction_cost'] = np.nan
key_info = ['from','tickLower', 'tickUpper']

for co in tqdm(collect):
    flag = 0
    if transaction.loc[co-1,'event_name']=='Burn':
        if transaction.loc[co-2,'event_name']=='Burn':
            flag=1
        transaction.loc[co,'fee_earned_token1'] = transaction.loc[co,'amount1_collected'] + transaction.loc[co-1-flag,'amount1_delta']
        transaction.loc[co,'fee_earned_token0'] = transaction.loc[co,'amount0_collected'] + transaction.loc[co-1-flag,'amount0_delta']
    else:
        continue
    possible_mi = transaction.loc[mint,:].loc[(transaction.loc[co,key_info]==transaction.loc[mint,key_info]).sum(axis=1)==3].index
    possible_mi = possible_mi[possible_mi<co]
    possible_b = transaction.loc[burn,:].loc[(transaction.loc[co,key_info]==transaction.loc[burn,key_info]).sum(axis=1)==3].index
    possible_b = possible_b[possible_b<co]
    if possible_mi.empty:
        continue
    mi = max(possible_mi)
    transaction.loc[co,'burn_dt'] = transaction.loc[co,'timeStamp'] - transaction.loc[mi,'timeStamp']
transaction.loc[burn,'burn_value_usdc'] = (transaction.loc[burn,'amount0_delta']/10**6 + transaction.loc[burn,'amount1_delta']/(1.0001**transaction.loc[burn,'p_current']/10**12))
transaction.loc[mint,'mint_value_usdc'] = (transaction.loc[mint,'amount0_delta']/10**6 + transaction.loc[mint,'amount1_delta']/(1.0001**transaction.loc[mint,'p_current']/10**12))
transaction.loc[collect,'fee_earned_usdc'] = transaction.loc[collect,'fee_earned_token1']/(1.0001**transaction.loc[collect,'p_current']/10**12) + transaction.loc[collect,'fee_earned_token0']/10**6 
transaction['wealth'] = transaction['amount0_delta']/10**6 +transaction['amount1_delta']/(1.0001**transaction['p_current']/10**12)
transaction.loc[swap,'wealth'] = 0
transaction.loc[collect,'wealth'] = 0
transaction['cum_wealth'] = transaction.groupby(info)['wealth'].cumsum()
transaction['liquidity_delta'].fillna(0,inplace=True)
transaction['cum_liquidity'] = transaction.groupby(info)['liquidity_delta'].cumsum()
transaction.to_csv(indir+'\\'+file_2)

Data description¶

Variable Description
principal 把mint视为以当时价投入本金，burn视为以当时价撤本金。此处本金取在此position投入的累计本金最大值
dt(hour) 某LP在此position的第一个action和最后一个action时间差
pnl (USD) pnl = fee_earned + wealth change - transaction cost
APR (%) pnl年化，APR = pnl/principal/(dt/24/365)*100
cum_transaction(USD) 该position付给矿工的总transaction cost(含mint，burn，collect）
transaction_return(%) transaction cost年化，transaction_return = cum_transaction/principal/(dt/24/365)*100
cum_fee(USD) 该position赚取的总手续费
fee_return(%) cum_fee年化，fee_return = cum_fee/principal/(dt/24/365)*100
cum_wealth_change(USD) LP在pool中token的总价值变化(collect时-mint时)
wealth_return (%) cum_wealth_change，wealth_return = cum_wealth_change/principal/(dt/24/365)*100
act_count 在该position action总数
outbound_flag 是否有mint时price不在所设定的区间内的，是则为True
center_deviation position的中点偏离mint时价格占position宽度的比例，如有多个mint则取多个mint的平均数
tick_range 该position宽度，tick_range = tickUpper - tickLower

cleared_position = tar
cleared = pd.DataFrame(index=tar)
cleared['principal'] = transaction.groupby(['from','tickUpper','tickLower'])['cum_wealth'].max().loc[cleared_position]
cleared['dt'] = (transaction.groupby(['from','tickUpper','tickLower'])['timeStamp'].max() - transaction.groupby(['from','tickUpper','tickLower'])['timeStamp'].min()).apply(lambda x:x.total_seconds()).loc[cleared_position]/3600
cleared['cum_transaction'] = transaction.groupby(['from','tickUpper','tickLower'])['transaction_cost_usdc'].sum().loc[cleared_position]
cleared['transaction_return'] = cleared['cum_transaction']/cleared['principal']/(cleared['dt']/24/365)*100
cleared['cum_fee'] = transaction.loc[collect].groupby(info)['fee_earned_usdc'].sum().loc[cleared_position]
cleared['fee_return'] = cleared['cum_fee']/cleared['principal']/(cleared['dt']/24/365)*100
cleared['cum_wealth_change'] = (-transaction.groupby(info)['burn_value_usdc'].sum() - transaction.groupby(info)['mint_value_usdc'].sum()).loc[tar]
cleared['wealth_return'] = cleared['cum_wealth_change']/cleared['principal']/(cleared['dt']/24/365)*100
cleared['cum_pnl'] = cleared['cum_fee'] + cleared['cum_wealth_change'] - cleared['cum_transaction']
cleared['APR'] = cleared['cum_pnl']/cleared['principal']/(cleared['dt']/24/365)*100
cleared['act_count'] = transaction.groupby(['from','tickUpper','tickLower'])['transactionCost'].count().loc[cleared_position]
cleared['outbound_flag'] = transaction.loc[mint].groupby(info)['outbound_flag'].sum().loc[cleared_position]>0
cleared['center_deviation'] = transaction.loc[mint].groupby(info)['center_deviation'].mean().loc[cleared_position]
cleared['tick_range'] =  cleared.index.map(lambda x:x[1]-x[2])
cleared['lastPx'] = transaction.groupby(info).tail(1).set_index(info).loc[tar,'p_current']
cleared['mint_amount1'] = transaction.groupby(info)['mint_amount1'].sum().loc[tar]
cleared['bench_wealth_change'] = transaction.groupby(info)['mint_amount0'].sum().loc[tar]/10**6-transaction.groupby(info)['mint_value_usdc'].sum().loc[tar]
cleared['bench_wealth_change'] += cleared['mint_amount1']/(1.0001**cleared['lastPx']/10**12)
cleared.to_csv(indir+'\\'+file_2.split('.')[0]+'_position.csv')

1.1 时间间隔对收益的影响¶

按时间间隔的quantile分成high(>75%)，midium high(50%-75%)，midium low(25%-50%)，low(<25%)

  • 时间越长赚取的手续费总数越多，但手续费年化越低
  • wealth change在绝对值和年化上均总体表现为时间短的更好
  • 大部分position都只有3个action，时间变长后action数量略微有增加，transaction cost略有增加,transaction cost年化显著降低
  • 总收益年化在75%分位点随时间间隔增加而显著降低

1.2 价格区间对收益的影响¶

  • 价格区间宽的持有时间更长
  • 收取的手续费随价格区间递增，年化随价格区间递减
  • transaction cost差距不大
  • 价格区间宽的亏时亏更多，赚时也赚更多

outbound_flag¶

是否有mint时current price不在所设定的区间内的，是则为True

  • 20.6%的position没有设在当前价格旁边
  • 在pnl和APR上未设在价格旁边的position表现更差
  • transaction cost区别不大
  • 赚取的手续费设在价格旁边的更多
  • welath change上分层不明显
  • 设在价格旁边的position倾向于把区间设得更宽

Center deviation¶

position的中点偏离当前价格占position宽度的比例

  • 在pnl和APR上偏离大于50%的表现显著差于其他（H）
  • transaction cost区别不大
  • 偏离小的赚取的手续费更多
  • 偏离小的wealth change亏的更多也赚的更多
  • 偏离小的所设区间更窄

1.3 年化收益率高的position特点分析¶

  • fee earned年化更高
  • wealth change基本为正值
  • 持有时间短（基本短于2天）

Liquidity distribution¶

Following graphs shows the liquidity and deposited token amount within certain tick interval with tick length 60. x is the left side of the tick interval. For the interval [tick,tick+60], the deposited token amount is calculated as: $$USDC = Liquidity_{tick,tick+60}\times(\frac{1}{\sqrt(1.0001^{tick}/10^{12})} -\frac{1}{\sqrt(1.0001^{tick+60}/10^{12})})\ if\ tick > current tick$$ $$USDC = Liquidity_{tick,tick+60}\times(\sqrt(1.0001^{tick+60}/10^{12}) -\sqrt(1.0001^{tick}/10^{12}))/1.0001^{current tick}/10^{12}\ if\ tick < current tick$$

In [115]:
tran = pd.read_csv(indir+'\\'+file,low_memory=False)
time_1 = 2000
LD1 = tran.loc[:time_1,['tickLower','tickUpper','event_name','liquidity_delta']]
time = datetime.fromtimestamp(tran.loc[time_1,'timeStamp'])
current = math.log(float(tran.loc[time_1,'sqrtPriceX96'])/2**96,1.0001)*2
del tran
LD1.drop(index = LD1[LD1['event_name'].isin(['Collect','Swap','Initialize'])].index,inplace=True)
LD1['liquidity_delta'] = LD1['liquidity_delta'].apply(lambda x:int(x)/10**12)
LD1_position = LD1.groupby(['tickLower','tickUpper'])['liquidity_delta'].sum().to_frame()
LD1_position['tickLower'] = LD1_position.index.map(lambda x:x[0])
LD1_position['tickUpper'] = LD1_position.index.map(lambda x:x[1])
LD1_position.drop(index=LD1_position[LD1_position['liquidity_delta']==0].index)
LD1_liquidity = pd.DataFrame(index=range(int(LD1_position['tickLower'].min()),int(LD1_position['tickUpper'].max()),60))
LD1_liquidity['liquidity']=0
for row in LD1_position.values:
    L,low,upper = row
    LD1_liquidity.loc[int(low):int(upper)-60,'liquidity'] = L + LD1_liquidity.loc[int(low):int(upper)-60,'liquidity']
m_price = LD1_liquidity.index[LD1_liquidity['liquidity'].argmax()]
fig,axes = plt.subplots(2,2,constrained_layout=True,figsize=(15,6))
axes[0][0].plot(LD1_liquidity)
axes[0][0].set_xlabel('tick_price')
axes[0][0].set_ylabel('liquidity')
axes[0][0].set_xlim([175000,225000])
axes[0][0].set_title('Time:{}, Current Tick Price: {:.2f},Max tick: {}'.format(time,current,m_price))
sm.qqplot(LD1_liquidity['liquidity'].values,fit=True,ax=axes[0][1])
axes[0][1].set_title('QQplot: against normal distribution'.format(time,current,m_price))
USDC_amount = LD1_liquidity.reset_index()
def cal_deposit(x):
    tick_low,L = x
    if tick_low>current:
        return L*(1/math.sqrt(1.0001**(tick_low)/10**12)-1/math.sqrt(1.0001**(tick_low+60)/10**12))
    else:
        return L*(math.sqrt(1.0001**(tick_low+60)/10**12)-math.sqrt(1.0001**(tick_low)/10**12))/(1.0001**(tick_low+30)/10**12)
USDC_amount['USDC'] = USDC_amount.apply(lambda x:cal_deposit(x),axis=1)
axes[1][0].plot(USDC_amount['index'],USDC_amount['USDC'])
axes[1][0].set_xlabel('tick_price')
axes[1][0].set_ylabel('Deposit amount (USD)')
axes[1][0].set_xlim([175000,225000])
axes[1][0].set_title('Time:{}, Current Tick Price: {:.2f},Max tick: {}'.format(time,current,m_price))
sm.qqplot(USDC_amount['USDC'].values,stats.exponnorm,fit=True,ax=axes[1][1])
axes[1][1].set_title('QQplot: against exponential normal distribution'.format(time,current,m_price))
